metadata.name: The Dip I
metadata.description:
The Dip collection is inspired by Qajar paintings and renowned crypto dip.

The true reason for it being labelled The Dip is as the Qajar era is travelling from the past to the present through the dip. 

"Buy the Dip" has become a common saying in crypto and it results in a brighter future for when prices recover and soar higher. Through the dip The Qajar Era comes to the present and the crypto dip enables for a brighter future.
